Title: Work Order: Dominance Offensive I
Description:
<Yoon's writing decorates the page though his feelings seem conflicted.>

I normally try to stay out of conflict, but an order is an order. Since you are of the Horde I decided to pass this order your way.

The Dominance Offensive has requested an order of red blossom leeks.

The troops down there just can't seem to get enough of them!
ObjectivesText: Plant 8 Red Blossom Leek Seeds on Sunsong Ranch.
